            <title>[LU-2839] Client file locking issue</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2839</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Customer experienced an issue with file locking.&lt;br/&gt;
This case is the same as &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1126&quot; title=&quot;Client file locking issue. Assertion triggered when decrementing a read lock on an item that has no existing read locks.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1126&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1126&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
Please increase priority to release a patch.&lt;br/&gt;
This is customer with payed Lustre support for env. size of 8 OSS.&lt;br/&gt;
